description._content: Description: Palestine Rlys - Stone Crushing Plant at Nur El Shams Quarry opened by Messrs Ahmed Nosrat & Co. Location: Palestine Date: 1922 Description: Sinai Military Rly. Traffic Offices Kantara (Type of Building erected as Staff Quarters on S.M.Rly at Intermediate Stations). Location: Palestine Date: 1922 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/733 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
